com.camerontec.catalys.util.dictionary

Interface IFieldGroupInfo

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IMessageComponent
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FieldGroupInfo

    public interface IFieldGroupInfo
extends IMessageComponent
    This is a definition for field groups. Field groups contain lists of message fields (fields with message context) and other message field groups.
    Author:
    Wes Hallman
